#: .\items.json
msgid "shopping brochure"
msgid_plural "shopping brochures"
msgstr[0] "购物宣传册"

#. ~ Use action message for {'str': 'shopping brochure'}.
#: .\items.json
msgid "You add the mall to your map."
msgstr "你将商场添加到了地图上。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'shopping brochure'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"This is a brochure advertising a local shopping mall.  It includes a map "
"with bus routes.  The buses aren't running but the roads should still be "
"there."
msgstr "这是一份宣传当地购物商场的宣传册。内含带公交路线的地图。公交车已停运，但道路应该还在。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Randomized Mall"
msgstr "随机化商场"

#. ~ Description for Randomized Mall
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Replaces the existing mall with one having a randomized layout.  Less "
"realistic looking but more variety."
msgstr "将现有商场替换为布局随机化的版本。外观真实性稍差，但提供了更多变化。"

#: .\overmap_terrain.json
msgid "parking lot"
msgstr "停车场"

#: .\overmap_terrain.json
msgid "shopping mall"
msgstr "购物中心"

#. ~ Name for scenario 'Mall Cop' for a male character
#: .\scenario.json
msgctxt "scenario_male"
msgid "Mall Cop"
msgstr "商场保安"

#. ~ Name for scenario 'Mall Cop' for a female character
#: .\scenario.json
msgctxt "scenario_female"
msgid "Mall Cop"
msgstr "商场保安"

#. ~ Description for scenario 'Mall Cop' for a male character.
#: .\scenario.json
msgctxt "scen_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You've survived for as long as you could inside of the mall you worked at as"
" a security guard.  Find a way out and try your best to survive."
msgstr "你作为保安，在你工作的商场内尽可能长时间地生存了下来。找到出路，并尽力活下去。"

#. ~ Description for scenario 'Mall Cop' for a female character.
#: .\scenario.json
msgctxt "scen_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You've survived for as long as you could inside of the mall you worked at as"
" a security guard.  Find a way out and try your best to survive."
msgstr "你作为保安，在你工作的商场内尽可能长时间地生存了下来。找到出路，并尽力活下去。"

